article_title: Sanborn grad's senior leadership forms heart of a champion
article_text:
Jed Magnusson of Kingston, a senior defender at Endicott College, led the Gulls to the ECAC Division III soccer championship this season. Magnusson is a Sanborn Regional High graduate. (Courtesy)

Sanborn grad's senior leadership forms heart of a champion

article_metadata.description: Before the Endicott men's soccer season began last fall, senior Jed Magnusson spoke to his teammates and said that he wanted the team to feel like a brotherhood this year.
